plot: The action picks up with Britt and Kaitlyn anxiously awaiting the results of the men's vote. Chris Harrison prepares to give good news to one Bachelorette and, sadly, bad news to the other woman. One stunning beauty is left speechless with the exciting announcement that she is, indeed, the Bachelorette. Then, the chosen Bachelorette continues to spend time getting to know the men better before the season's first rose ceremony.
